### Get Teacher Dashboard stats (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get Teacher's own lessons (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get Teacher's own groups (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/my-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get lesson statistics for a specific lesson (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{lesson_public_id}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get lesson statistics — 401 (no token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{lesson_public_id}}/stats

### Get detailed lesson result for a student (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{lesson_public_id}}/students/{{student_public_id}}/result
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get detailed lesson result for a student — 401 (no token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{lesson_public_id}}/students/{{student_public_id}}/result

### Get detailed lesson result for a student — 404 LESSON_NOT_FOUND
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{invalid_lesson_public_id}}/students/{{student_public_id}}/result
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get detailed lesson result for a student — 403 STUDENT_NO_ACCESS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/lessons/{{lesson_public_id}}/students/{{unauthorized_student_public_id}}/result
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get Teacher's own students (Requires TEACHER)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Create student in teacher's own group — sends invitation email (Requires TEACHER, groupPublicId mandatory)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher.created@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Create student - missing groupPublicId (400 VALIDATION_FAILED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher.nogroup@example.com"
}

### Create student - forbidden (ADMIN token -> 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin.attempt@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Resend invitation to INVITED student (Teacher)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students/{{student_public_id}}/resend-invite
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Resend invitation - student not owned (403 Forbidden)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students/{{unauthorized_student_public_id}}/resend-invite
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Update student in teacher's own group (Requires TEACHER, groupPublicId mandatory)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students/{{student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_student",
  "email": "updated.student@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Update student - foreign teacher group (400 INVALID_ROLE_FOR_GROUP)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students/{{student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_student",
  "email": "updated.student@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "missing-group-public-id"
}

### Update student - student not owned (403 Forbidden)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher/students/{{unauthorized_student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hacked_student",
  "email": "hacked@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}
